title: No.Country.For.Old.Men-CIPSP
description:
No Country For Old Men





CIPSP


High quality psp movies :

- Always high quality rips from DVD, HD-DVD or Blu-ray

- Always correct aspect ratio, no cropping or weird stretching crap

- Always optimized sound for PSP, never too low sound.



Put the files in your video folder on the memorystick.

Tested on firmware 3.90



Some movies are shot in 2,35:1 aspect ratio which is wider than the psp 

screen and therefore you will see black bars. You can be a lamer and remove 

these by pressing TRIANGLE then press SCREEN MODE once.
